### GitHub webhook (push)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cicd/webhook
X-GitHub-Event: push
X-Hub-Signature-256: sha256=dummy
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ref": "refs/heads/main",
  "after": "0123456789abcdef",
  "repository": { "name": "sample-app" }
}

### GitHub webhook (release published)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/cicd/webhook
X-GitHub-Event: release
X-Hub-Signature-256: sha256=dummy
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "published",
  "release": { "tag_name": "v1.2.3" },
  "repository": { "name": "sample-app" }
}

